<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Migración de Equipos</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <meta name="csrf-token" content="<%= csrfToken %>">
    <style>
        body { background-color: #f4f7f6; }
        .loader-overlay {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); z-index: 1050;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
        }
        .step-card {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: .75rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0,0,0, .05);
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .step-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .step-header .step-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--bs-primary);
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }
        .step-header h2 {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }
        #summary-container .list-group-item {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="loader-overlay d-none" id="loader">
    <div class="spinner-border text-primary" role="status" style="width: 3rem; height: 3rem;"></div>
    <p class="mt-3 fs-5">Procesando, por favor espera...</p>
</div>

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-header">
            <i class="bi bi-funnel-fill step-icon"></i>
            <div>
                <h2>Paso 1: Seleccionar Contrato</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Elige una empresa y un contrato con equipos pendientes de migración.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <label for="empresa-select" class="form-label fw-bold">Empresa</label>
                <select id="empresa-select" class="form-select form-select-lg"></select>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <label for="contrato-select" class="form-label fw-bold">Contrato</label>
                <select id="contrato-select" class="form-select form-select-lg" disabled></select>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="step-2-card" class="step-card d-none">
        <div class="step-header">
            <i class="bi bi-clipboard2-data-fill step-icon"></i>
             <div>
                <h2>Paso 2: Revisar Resumen y Migrar</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Verifica los datos y procede con la migración al inventario principal.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="summary-container" class="mb-4">
            </div>
        <div id="action-container" class="text-end">
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
<script src="/js/soportemigracion.js"></script>
</body>
</html>